information: MS BUSINESS is a company based in Cergy, near to Paris, France. Specialising in the import-export of articles from Europe to Africa, we are on the lookout for Europe-based suppliers for companies based Africa. We are also interested in sourcing raw material and commodities on behalf of European manufacturers. We also supply a wide range of products, such as mangoes, groundnuts, and cashew nuts that we import from countries in sub-Saharan Africa (Senegal, Guinea, Côte d’Ivoire, etc.). Our specialities: - trading in foodstuffs, - import / export unregulated products of all types, - purchase and sale of vehicles and spare parts, - comprehensive freight services, - consulting, - business finding, - trading in construction materials. Don't hesitate to get in touch to find out more about all the different services that we offer. Our sales team will answer you as quickly as possible to satisfy your request.
